<div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 8px;">
  <div style="font-weight: bold; min-width: 40px;">Q13.</div>
  <div style="flex: 1;">
::: {.question-block}
<form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); checkAnswer('module2_mcq_q13')" data-correct-answer="D">
<strong style="display: block;">Which risk is NOT eliminated through diversification?</strong>
<label><input type="radio" name="module2_mcq_q13" value="A"> A. Firm-specific risk</label><br>
<label><input type="radio" name="module2_mcq_q13" value="B"> B. Idiosyncratic risk</label><br>
<label><input type="radio" name="module2_mcq_q13" value="C"> C. Diversifiable risk</label><br>
<label><input type="radio" name="module2_mcq_q13" value="D"> D. Systematic risk</label><br>
<label><input type="radio" name="module2_mcq_q13" value="E"> E. Unique risk</label><br>
</form>
<div id="feedback-module2_mcq_q13" class="feedback" data-status="" style="display:none;">
‚úÖ Correct: D. Systematic risk cannot be eliminated by diversification.
</div>
